Sorin is found east of the of Burgh de Rott. Like all citizens, he will praise the player for their role in In Aid of the Myreque. He can be found on the eastern side of the village just outside Aurel's Supplies.

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • There is an unused version of Sorin in the game cache, who has a different appearance that looks identical to Wiskit.
